<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>

<canvas id="myCanvas" width="300" height="150" style="border:1px solid #d3d3d3;">
Your browser does not support the HTML5 canvas tag.
</canvas>

<p>请试着把 miterLimit 设置为 4。如果斜接长度超过 miterLimit 的值，边角会以 lineJoin 的 "bevel" 类型来显示。</p>

<script>

var c=document.getElementById("myCanvas");
var ctx=c.getContext("2d");
ctx.lineWidth=10;
ctx.lineJoin="miter";
ctx.miterLimit=5;
ctx.moveTo(20,20);
ctx.lineTo(50,27);
ctx.lineTo(20,34);
ctx.stroke();

</script>

</body>
</html>